n-based soul trio\nBULLET::::- Capitol (Williamsburg, Virginia), a historic building that housed the House of Burgesses of the Colony of Virginia 1705–1779\n\nBULLET::::- Capital (disambiguation)\nBULLET::::- Capitol Hill (disambiguation), a number of districts in the United States and Canada\nBULLET::::- Capitol station (disambiguation)\nBULLET::::- Capitol Theater (disambiguation), a number of former and current cinemas or theatres located throughout the world\nBULLET::::- Le Capitole (train), a former express train between Paris and Toulouse\n"}
